Package com.crawljax.core.state

This is the core package for the state machine.

See:
          Description

Class Summary
Attribute This class represents a attribute of a Element.
CrawlPath The Path a Crawler has taken, or is about to backtrack on.
Element This class represents an element.
Eventable Eventable class: an element having an event attached to it (onclick, onmouseover, ...) so that it can change the DOM state.
Identification The Identification class, this class is used to denote a specific element.
StateFlowGraph The State-Flow Graph is a directed graph with states on the vertices and clickables on the edges.
StateMachine The State Machine.
StateVertix The state vertix class which represents a state in the browser.
 

Enum Summary

Identification.How The method used for identifying elements on the DOM tree.
